<s> A pharmacy technician once qualified has to register as a professional on the General Pharmaceutical Council register . <\s>
<s> The GPhC is the governing body for pharmacy health care professionals and this is who regulates the practice of pharmacists and pharmacy technicians . <\s>
<s> In Ancient Greece , Diocles of Carystus was one of several men studying the medicinal properties of plants . <\s>
<s> He wrote several treatises on the topic . <\s>
<s> The Greek physician Pedanius Dioscorides is famous for writing a five volume book in his native Greek Περί ύλης ιατρικής in the 1st century AD . <\s>
<s> The Latin translation De Materia Medica was used a basis for many medieval texts , and was built upon by many middle eastern scientists during the Islamic Golden Age . <\s>
