<s> Of great impact were also the works by al-Maridini of Baghdad and Cairo , and Ibn al-Wafid , both of which were printed in Latin more than fifty times , appearing as De Medicinis universalibus et particularibus by ' Mesue ' the younger , and the Medicamentis simplicibus by ' Abenguefit ' . <\s>
