<s> In 1564 , René Goulaine de Laudonnière established the first European settlement , Fort Caroline , on the St. Johns near the main village of the Saturiwa . <\s>
<s> Philip II of Spain ordered Pedro Menéndez de Avilés to protect the interest of Spain by attacking the French presence at Fort Caroline . <\s>
