<s> Union forces then retreated to Jacksonville and held the city for the remainder of the war . <\s>
<s> In March 1864 a Confederate cavalry confronted a Union expedition resulting in the Battle of Cedar Creek . <\s>
<s> Warfare and the long occupation left the city disrupted after the war . <\s>
