<s> Imperialism has played an important role in the histories of Japan , Korea , the Assyrian Empire , the Chinese Empire , the Roman Empire , Greece , the Byzantine Empire , the Persian Empire , the Ottoman Empire , Ancient Egypt , the British Empire , India , and many other empires . <\s>
