<s> The Age of Imperialism , a time period beginning around 1700 , saw industrializing nations engaging in the process of colonizing , influencing , and annexing other parts of the world in order to gain political power . <\s>
<s> Although imperialist practices have existed for thousands of years , the term `` Age of Imperialism '' generally refers to the activities of European powers from the early 18th century through to the middle of the 20th century , for example , the `` The Great Game '' in Persian lands , the `` Scramble for Africa '' and the `` Open Door Policy '' in China . <\s>
<s> During the 20th century , historians John Gallagher and Ronald Robinson constructed a framework for understanding European imperialism . <\s>
